{"tid":940978,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老】【聖誕快樂】施永青：CCL肯定未跌夠 樓價明年首季有支持","createTime":"2018-12-14T11:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T04:11:04.000Z","uid":216432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"478ec0e89bb34b12687fddff94ccd1be950c731a","tid":940978,"uid":216432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181214/59030402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F59030402&d=ntJutaLORMfbBelMl%2FE2uIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3622827a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F59030402&h=1335fd28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181214/59030402</a><br />\n中原集團主席兼總裁施永青表示，設計中原大灣區指數是為整個大灣區建立一個生態環境，可以產生更多協同效應。他又指，指數不會受外力影響，將真實的情況呈現給社會知道，有個參考指標，「亦都希望中央可以睇到啲真野」。<br />\n不過他認為，大灣區樓市對港人吸引力不大，由於個別三、四線城市樓價早前升幅多了，所以明年向下趨勢較大，料有5%至8%回落。<br />\n對於香港的樓市，他指，現時出現回落，不是香港樓市本身出現問題，而是受中美貿易戰影響，導致本港投資者入市審慎，預期是次樓市調整會維持一段長時間。他說：「第一級踩落黎起碼（二手市場）跌10%至15%，明年第一季便會找到支持&hellip;&hellip;中原城市領先指數CCL肯定未跌夠。」<br />\n對於本港樓市何時重新恢復投資熱情，他表示，「要中國經濟作出一定調整，開始重新搵到新的增長動力，如今處於L形經濟，料最快三年才可恢復增長動力。」他建議政府把握這次樓市調整的時期，趁機修改逆周期措施。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181214/large/1544782601_6521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F1544782601_6521.jpg&h=a1d69ef8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f8586e9475a8e30149835292ac9e2128d54992c","tid":940978,"uid":17866,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"Ccl大統領竟然唱淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小心出街比低智仔斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f568761be31b242628f20738d3e90527b3ebc30f","tid":940978,"uid":119313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"老施講緊三年跌30%，其實都唔算睇得好淡"},{"pid":"2c3703c9afd652e2b84fefcc86988d9638966f07","tid":940978,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"邊個公屋廢老學人講樓? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318c55e65bd5f9b3d44347db986def1f86317a2b","tid":940978,"uid":28245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"一人一張聖誕卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1049a3b7c0efa7b432cf37dc1c69d03e3b1388c","tid":940978,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"痴老母啲公營盦位住嘅廢淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b8eef216543ed03c789ba19825f87ed5a59e84","tid":940978,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fafd377a3a73e196295e4c7e3050fb1424b88321","tid":940978,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b8eef216543ed03c789ba19825f87ed5a59e84","tid":940978,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"佢16頭都睇跌，到16中就轉口風話自己睇錯"},{"pid":"c9e9e98d270af0e30bb0a86ae8283a9a5212af4c","tid":940978,"uid":20256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"見升睇升<br />\n見跌睇跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b75d389b7e3e22562c8c0e1585002d1d4b95e94","tid":940978,"uid":78791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"faed2fa5904d7379ed44f8dfdc0a243cab84afc2","tid":940978,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi